Cabbages are a series of unobtainable items. Presumably, they are used in order to track the status of players being able to purchase exclusive content. However, it is unknown how they are used in this regard.

  • Two cabbages were added in June 2018, with "Buy" and "Unbuy" versions, with the release of the Purple skin exclusive to Twitch Prime
  • A cabbage was added in November 2019, to track points earned in the Twisted League, and presumably determining access to the Leagues Reward Shop
  • Another cabbage was added on 5 December 2019, with the overhaul of the Leagues Reward Shop, tracking "negative points"
  • Four cabbages were added in October 2020, presumably used during the Trailblazer League
  • Two cabbages were added in January 2022, presumably used during the Shattered Relics League
